data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 11541 Merejildo Madrid, nestled in the picturesque Sandstone Ranch community. This enchanting property offers a blend of elegance, comfort, and modern living that is sure to captivate you. Key features includes open concept kitchen. Step into a spacious, open kitchen equipped with all modern appliances, including refrigerator. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or just love to entertain, this kitchen is perfect for both everyday living and special occasions. The spiral staircase leads you to all the bedrooms, creating a captivating focal point within the home. Upstairs, you'll find a convenient utility room that streamlines your daily chores and adds an extra layer of practicality to your living space. The master bathroom is a true sanctuary with a jetted soaking tub and a walk-in shower. The mountain views from the master and backyard are breathtaking. With no neighbors behind, you can really take in and appreciate nature's beauty.
